			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-448089">
									

<p>Thanks Grey. I have no idea as to how to finish it, but I did want to demonstrate his impotence with regards to everyone thinking he's overpowered. A bullet to the head kills him just as easily as anyone else.</p>
<p>Though I think he gets kinda emo-y at the middle and stuff, and there's little other things that just kinda bug me.</p>
<p>Oh, and for the detail about his day, I kinda wanted to imply that ninety percent of the time, he didn't have anything of interest to do, and that one of his major problems is that he's going even crazier from boredom, because he's stuck in a place he hates, with people he hates, in a world that he would probably find more interesting if it was on fire.</p>
<p>But yeah, more stuff would be kinda better from a reading point of view.</p>

							</div>

								
					
